{"title":"台阶","authors":["靳亚利"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"台阶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靳亚利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命是一个过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是向前，向上的过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一层坚实的台阶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶上开满了鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶上长遍了绿树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶上缀结着硕果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶上厚铺着冰雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶似乎很窄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眨眼就走了过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶感觉很宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需付出全力去跋涉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶留在心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竖起了纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的台阶丢在身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被渐渐遗忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中途，有一层台阶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着你那日夜思念的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往前走，还有一层台阶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬挂着闪亮的奖章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往前走，再往前走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是夕阳还是朝阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在最后那层台阶上"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}